</div>
<div>The Bow Dress is a study in refined minimalism, crafted for those who value form and function in equal measure. Its sleek black silhouette is designed to endure—both in style and wear—offering a versatile piece that transitions effortlessly across occasions. Wide straps provide comfort and support, while the subtle bow detail at the chest, secured with a single button, adds a quiet yet distinctive focal point. The ruched lower half introduces a soft texture, ensuring the design remains dynamic without excess.</div>
