<div class="markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark">
<p>The shoulders are adorned with delicate ribbons of fine strings, cascading gracefully to add a soft yet dynamic movement to the overall silhouette. These strings serve as both a functional and aesthetic feature, framing the shoulders and complementing the dress's flowing form. The combination of modern design techniques and timeless sophistication makes this dress not only a striking visual statement but also a deeply personal gift, embodying André's admiration for Cindy.</p>
</div>
